data.description: This 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath Charmer With A Large Front Courtyard Is A MUST SEE!! Enter Into The Spacious Living Room Which Offers; A Large Garden Window & Tons Of Natural Light. Continue Through The Dining Area To The Kitchen Which Offers All White Appliances & Tons Of Cabinet Space! The Open Floor Plan Makes This A Perfect Space For Family Gatherings. Laundry Room Off Of The Kitchen. The Primary Bedroom Offers; Tons Of Space, An En Suite Bath & Access To The Front Courtyard. Ceiling Fans & Neutral Paint Throughout! The Spacious Courtyard Offers Tons Of Entertainment Potential, Perfect For Those Summer BBQs w/Friends & Family! Conveniently Located To Shopping and Several Parks Including Pioneer Park & Kellogg Zaher Sports Complex. Minutes From Us 95 Making Getting Around Quick & Easy!
